## Content Pipeline States

```
idea-bank.md  →  drafts/  →  scheduled/  →  published/
                                              ↓
                                         post-mortems.md
```

**Rule:** Nothing moves to `scheduled/` without the Two-Pass Review (see `_PATTERNS/two-pass-review.md`):
- **Craft Pass** — hook lands / promise specific / skimmable / stance / CTA / length / 4Cs
- **Voice Pass** — banned-word audit clean / rhythm / punctuation / register / no LLM tells

**Rule:** Nothing moves to `published/` without being actually published (status-honest).
**Rule:** After publish + 48h, append engagement notes to `post-mortems.md`.

