## Hook Generation Protocol

When I ask for a hook / opener / scroll-stopper:
1. Generate 5 options across 5 different frames (reframe, parallel declaration, paradox, conditional reveal, negation flip)
2. Each ≤10 words
3. Mark the one most on-voice
4. Ask which direction to develop, don't pick unilaterally

